snippet.title: Farland Story (PC 98) (English) Playthrough Part 1
snippet.description:
http://www.pandemoniumsoftworks.com

Part 1 of my Playthrough of Farland Story in English for the NEC PC-98.

My only complaint so far is the font. Some of the letters don't look like the the letter they are supposed to resemble, most specifically the letter m.

Anyway the game is fun and quite easy so far.
